\begin_layout Proof
由于Schwartz不等式, 
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
|(x_{n},y_{n})-(x,y)| & \leq|(x_{n},y_{n})-(x_{n},y)|+|(x_{n},y)-(x,y)|\\
 & =|(x_{n},y_{n}-y)|+(x_{n}-x,y)|\\
 & \leq||x_{n}||||y_{n}-y||+||x_{n}-x||||y||.
\end{align*}

